\section desc Description
Common utilities to manipulate and analyze particle candidates

\subsection interface Public interface
- AddFourMomenta: set up a composite reco::Candidate adding its daughters four-momenta and electric charge.
- Booster: boost a reco::Candidate by a specified boost vector. 
- ApplyEnergyCorrection: scale particle 4-momentum by a specified correction factor.
- NBodyCombiner: produces all possible candidate pairs specifying a configurable selection criteria, checking 
  for overlaps, and avoiding double-counting.
- CenterOfMassBooster: boost a reco::Candidate to its center-of-mass reference frame.
- Thrust: utility to compute thrust value and axis of a collection of reco::Candidates.

\subsection modules Modules
None.

\subsection tests Unit tests and examples
- <b>testThrust</b>: test Thrust utility.

